            <div class="col-xs-6 col-md-3"><h3 class="text-muted">Lumen</h3><img class="img-rounded" src="/images/lumen-logo.png" style="max-width: 176px"></div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>



<div class="container landing-container landing-container-last">
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
            <h2 class="text-center">Code Quality</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Full respect of modern coding standards: libraries comply with PSR-1, PSR-2, PSR-4 and PSR-7.</li>
                <li>Fully tested using PHPUnit.</li>
                <li>High performant code: Code is written with performance in mind.</li>
                <li>New releases follow semantic versioning since day one.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6  text-center">
